    "bbox": [
      58.32,
      618.46,
      533.94,
      671.5
    ],
    "text": "Fairly strong winds about (35-45) kmph can be expected at times over Western slopes of the central hills, Northern, North-central, North-western and Southern provinces and in Trincomalee district.",
