      61.34,
      504.34,
      557.81,
      539.23
    ],
    "text": "The wave height may increase about (2.0 \u2013 3.0) meters in the sea areas off the coast extending from Mannar to Pottuvil via Puttalam, Colombo, Galle and Hambantota (this is not for land area).",
